---
layout: base.njk
title: "Services | Sabdia Constructions"
description: "Full-spectrum luxury residential development services — design, development management, interior architecture, and expert construction by Sabdia Constructions, Brisbane."
extraCss: "<style>
.svc-detail-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:96px;align-items:center;padding:clamp(72px,10vw,140px) 0}
.svc-detail-grid:nth-child(even){direction:rtl}
.svc-detail-grid:nth-child(even)>*{direction:ltr}
.svc-detail-grid+.svc-detail-grid{border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.svc-detail-img{overflow:hidden;aspect-ratio:4/3}
.svc-detail-img img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;filter:saturate(.85);transition:transform .8s var(--ease)}
.svc-detail-grid:hover .svc-detail-img img{transform:scale(1.04)}
.svc-num{font-family:var(--font-d);font-size:clamp(80px,12vw,160px);font-weight:300;font-style:italic;color:rgba(158,139,106,.1);line-height:1;margin-bottom:-20px;display:block}
.svc-detail-h{font-family:var(--font-d);font-size:clamp(30px,4vw,52px);font-weight:300;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:20px;letter-spacing:-.02em}
.svc-detail-h em{font-style:italic;color:var(--gold)}
.svc-detail-p{font-size:13.5px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.9;color:var(--ink3);margin-bottom:16px}
.svc-detail-list{list-style:none;margin-top:24px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:24px}
.svc-detail-list li{font-size:13px;font-weight:300;color:var(--ink3);padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
.svc-detail-list li::before{content:'';width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);flex-shrink:0}
@media(max-width:900px){.svc-detail-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:36px}.svc-detail-grid:nth-child(even){direction:ltr}}
</style>"
permalink: /services.html
---

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="page-hero">
  <img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/1cc2db_9e730867446c414c9fe72c1549cb7261~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_1920,h_1080,al_c,q_85/1cc2db_9e730867446c414c9fe72c1549cb7261~mv2.jpg" alt="Services" loading="eager">
  <div class="page-hero-ov"></div>
  <div class="page-hero-content inner">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--gold2);margin-bottom:16px"><span style="display:inline-block;width:24px;height:1px;background:var(--gold2);vertical-align:middle;margin-right:14px"></span>What We Offer</div>
    <h1 class="page-h">Our<br><em>Services</em></h1>
    <p class="page-hero-sub">Full-spectrum residential development expertise delivered entirely in-house.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INTRO -->
<section class="sp-sm" style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)">
  <div class="inner" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:72px;align-items:center">
    <div>
      <div class="slabel reveal">Integrated Approach</div>
      <h2 class="about-h reveal d1" style="font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,52px)">Every element,<br><em>under one roof</em>.</h2>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="about-p reveal d2">At Sabdia, we believe the best residential developments are those where design, development, and construction work as one seamless system — not as separate, disconnected disciplines. Our fully integrated in-house model is our defining advantage.</p>
      <p class="about-p reveal d2">From the first sketch to the final handover, every decision is made by the same team, with the same vision, and the same commitment to excellence.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICE DETAILS -->
<section class="sp">
  <div class="inner">
    {% for svc in services %}
    <div class="svc-detail-grid">
      <div class="svc-detail-img {% if loop.index % 2 == 1 %}reveal-x{% else %}reveal-r{% endif %}">
        <img src="{{ svc.image }}" alt="{{ svc.title }}" loading="lazy">
      </div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="svc-num">{{ svc.number }}</span>
        <div class="slabel">Service {{ ["One","Two","Three","Four"][loop.index0] }}</div>
        <h2 class="svc-detail-h">{{ svc.title | safe }}</h2>
        {% for para in svc.description_paragraphs %}
        <p class="svc-detail-p">{{ para }}</p>
        {% endfor %}
        <ul class="svc-detail-list">
          {% for item in svc.deliverables %}
          <li>{{ item }}</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PROCESS RECAP -->
<section class="sp" style="background:var(--bg2);border-top:1px solid var(--border)">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="slabel reveal" style="margin-bottom:56px">The Process</div>
    <div class="proc-track">
      <div class="proc-step reveal"><div class="proc-n">1</div><div class="proc-t">Design</div><div class="proc-d">Vision-led architectural and interior design, guided by site, context, and client aspiration.</div></div>
      <div class="proc-step reveal d1"><div class="proc-n">2</div><div class="proc-t">Develop</div><div class="proc-d">Comprehensive development management — approvals, planning, engineering, and finance.</div></div>
      <div class="proc-step reveal d2"><div class="proc-n">3</div><div class="proc-t">Construct</div><div class="proc-d">Master-level construction with premium materials and rigorous quality control at every stage.</div></div>
      <div class="proc-step reveal d3"><div class="proc-n">4</div><div class="proc-t">Deliver</div><div class="proc-d">Handover and aftercare — ensuring your home continues to exceed expectations.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="sp" style="background:var(--dark)">
  <div class="inner" style="text-align:center">
    <div class="slabel slabel-dark reveal" style="justify-content:center;margin-bottom:20px">Start Your Project</div>
    <h2 class="reveal d1" style="font-family:var(--font-d);font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,68px);font-weight:300;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:24px;letter-spacing:-.02em">Ready to build something <em style="color:var(--gold2)">remarkable</em>?</h2>
    <p class="reveal d2" style="font-size:13px;font-weight:300;color:rgba(253,252,248,.45);max-width:440px;margin:0 auto 40px;line-height:1.8">Whether you have a site, a vision, or simply a desire for exceptional living — we'd love to hear from you.</p>
    <div class="reveal d3" style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <a href="/contact.html" class="btn-p">Begin a Conversation</a>
      <a href="/properties/" class="btn-g btn-g-light">View Properties</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
